{"title_page": "Samir Fazlagi\u0107", "text_new": "{{short description|Norwegian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Samir Fazlagi\u0107\n| image    = \n| fullname = \n| height = {{height|m=1.86|precision=0}}\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1982|10|21}}\n| birth_place = [[\u010capljina]], [[SFR Yugoslavia]]\n| currentclub  = \n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Defender (football)|Defender]]\n| youthyears1= \n| youthclubs1= [[Stab\u00e6k Fotball|Stab\u00e6k]]\n| years1 = 2002\u20132005 | years2 = 2004 | years3 = 2005\u20132009 | years4 = 2010\u20132011 | years5 = 2011\u20132013\n| clubs1 = [[Stab\u00e6k Fotball|Stab\u00e6k]] | clubs2 = \u2192 [[Skeid Fotball|Skeid]] (''loan'') | clubs3 = [[Str\u00f8msgodset IF|Str\u00f8msgodset]] | clubs4 = [[Nybergsund IL-Trysil]] | clubs5 =[[KIL Toppfotball|Kongsvinger]]\n| caps1 = 23 | goals1 = 3 | caps2 = 11 | goals2 = 1 | caps3 = 86 | goals3 = 6 | caps4 = 27 | goals4 = 1 | caps5 = 48 | goals5 = 3\n| nationalyears1= 2003\n| nationalteam1=[[Norway U-21]]<ref name=\"fotball.no\">http://www.fotball.no/histstat.ASP?WCI=wiPerson&personid=2094474</ref>\n| nationalcaps1= 3 | nationalgoals1 = 1\n| pcupdate = 5 September 2012\n}}\n'''Samir Fazlagi\u0107'''  (born 21 October 1982) is a former professional [[Association football|football player]] who last played for [[KIL Toppfotball|Kongsvinger]]. He first played in [[Stab\u00e6k Fotball|Stab\u00e6k]].<ref name=\"fotball.aftenposten.no\">http://fotball.aftenposten.no/eliteserien/index.jsp?service=default&stats=true&type=person&personId=15658&</ref>\n\nFazlagi\u0107 has played three games for [[Norway national under-21 football team|Norways national under-21 football team]].<ref name=\"fotball.no\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.altomfotball.no/element.do?cmd=player&personId=32503 Samir Fazlagi\u0107] on Altomfotball {{in lang|no}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fazlagic, Samir}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1982 births]]\n[[Cat